{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/media-enquiries","content_id":"5f55dff1-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"Contact our press office if you’re a journalist with a media enquiry or interview request. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We cannot answer calls from individuals about benefit or pension claims. Please <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contact-jobcentre-plus\" class=\"govuk-link\">contact Jobcentre Plus</a> or <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contact-pension-service\" class=\"govuk-link\">contact The Pension Service</a> instead.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"national-and-local-media-enquiries-including-scotland-and-wales\">National and local media enquiries, including Scotland and Wales</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>DWP Press Office</strong><br>\nCaxton House<br>\nTothill Street<br>\nLondon<br>\nSW1H 9NA<br>\nE-mail: <a href=\"mailto:newsdesk@dwp.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">newsdesk@dwp.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Follow us on X <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://x.com/dwpgovuk\" class=\"govuk-link\">https://x.com/dwpgovuk</a></p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Updated the DWP press office phone number.","public_timestamp":"2023-05-11T08:00:00Z"},{"note":"Added Press Office email address for media enquiries.","public_timestamp":"2021-11-30T07:55:27Z"},{"note":"Temporarily updated DWP Press Office phone number. ","public_timestamp":"2021-11-01T16:54:37Z"},{"note":"Changed the press Office telephone number.","public_timestamp":"2021-05-13T07:00:01Z"},{"note":"There is now one telephone number for all national and local media enquiries.","public_timestamp":"2020-10-27T10:50:41Z"},{"note":"Updated phone number for Scotland local media enquiries. ","public_timestamp":"2018-04-06T15:09:39Z"},{"note":"Changed the out of hours number (journalists only) to 07 623 928 975.","public_timestamp":"2018-04-06T10:36:33Z"},{"note":"Added translation","public_timestam